      "rationale": "ANSYS Fluent 2023 R1 used with documented version control, ISO 9001 QMS in place at simulation facility, and full audit trail of simulation runs maintained."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Numerical code verification",
