      "acceptanceCriteria": "Solver must pass benchmark verification cases relevant to rotating machinery and viscous flow at MRL 2.",
      "rationale": "ANSYS Fluent verified against ASME V&V 20 benchmark cases for rotating disk flow and pipe flow; convergence to analytical solutions confirmed within 1% error."
