    "actor": "https://uofa.net/synth/actor/morrison-cfd-lab-lead",
    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "The credibility assessment is accepted at Medium assurance level for MRL 2. Seven of thirteen factors were formally assessed. Two factors — Discretization Error (GCI 11.3% vs 5% threshold) and Test Conditions (operating point outside validation envelope) — show achievedLevel below requiredLevel. The assessment team considers the overall evidence sufficient for the intended regulatory submission despite these shortfalls. No formal risk acceptance documentation or compensating controls were recorded for the below-threshold factors.",
